| **Rate Limiting** | No protection against abuse | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| **Error Handling** | Stack traces leak to clients | Add global error handler with env-aware messages |
| **404s** | Unmatched routes return default HTML | Add explicit 404 JSON handler |
| **Body Parsing** | None configured, no size limit | Add `express.json()` with `limit` |
| **Logging** | No request audit trail | Add `morgan` |
| **Data Exposure** | `/users` returns email addresses | Remove PII from unauthenticated endpoints |
| **Configuration** | Hardcoded port | Use `process.env.PORT` |

